  "title": "Operations Support Analyst- SK",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Use Microsoft Excel functions such as formulas, filtering, data validation, and pivot tables to manage and report data accurately</li><li>Read, understand, and write clear technical procedures, emails, and reports to support team communication and documentation</li><li>Apply strong attention to detail and a methodical approach to ensure data quality and follow process requirements</li><li>Operate basic computer software and learn new software tools and terminal-based applications to support daily tasks</li><li>Follow detailed written instructions and adapt to shift-based or scheduled maintenance work, including nights and weekends if required</li><li>Collaborate effectively with team members using clear communication to achieve shared goals</li><li>Apply basic knowledge of telecommunications or networking concepts, such as nodes, customer lines, and broadband, to support technical tasks</li><li>Demonstrate interest or experience in basic scripting or automation to improve work efficiency</li><li>Perform data entry and provide technical support based on prior experience</li></ul><p><strong>Work Location- Nearest MRT Tai Seng</strong><br /><strong>Contract Duration- 9 months</strong><br /><strong>Willing to work in shifts-(including nights/weekends if required)</strong></p>",
